Pair with different companion sources:
With Ñāṇavīra for existential structure.
With Nāgārjuna for emptiness.
With Ṭhānissaro for fabrication/practice.
With Levin-style cognition for rendering models.
With Corbin only cautiously, as contrast: imaginal ontology vs Buddhist de-imaginalization.
